{"tid":1516624,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★華為據報擬推新款高端手機或不能裝 Android、 Google與地圖","createTime":"2019-08-29T15:31:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-29T15:33:35.000Z","uid":19454,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"4babd726ce7ad4b188793e6935cf419758628d64","tid":1516624,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:31:42.000Z","msg":"&lt;匯港通訊&gt; 《路透》報道,中國電訊設備商華為計劃在歐洲推出新款高端智能手機,但或許<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">不能安裝 Google(谷歌)Android(安卓)平台與地圖。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n報道引述消息人士指,華為預備在9月18日推出 Mate 30 系列新版手機,適用於 5G 網絡,將是美國總統特朗普自5月中開始對華為實施制裁後,集團推出的首款智能手機。新手機是否配置 Android 平台,成為市場關注焦點。<br />\n<br />\nGoogle 發言人接受路透查詢時指出,Mate 30 將不可能配置 Google 開發的 Android 平台與地圖,因美國已經對華為作出禁制。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/news/%E8%8F%AF%E7%82%BA%E6%93%9A%E5%A0%B1%E6%93%AC%E6%8E%A8%E6%96%B0%E6%AC%BE%E9%AB%98%E7%AB%AF%E6%89%8B%E6%A9%9F%E6%88%96%E4%B8%8D%E8%83%BD%E8%A3%9D-android-002827694.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.yahoo.com%2Fnews%2F%25E8%258F%25AF%25E7%2582%25BA%25E6%2593%259A%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E6%2593%25AC%25E6%258E%25A8%25E6%2596%25B0%25E6%25AC%25BE%25E9%25AB%2598%25E7%25AB%25AF%25E6%2589%258B%25E6%25A9%259F%25E6%2588%2596%25E4%25B8%258D%25E8%2583%25BD%25E8%25A3%259D-android-002827694.html&d=uSpWWhS%2FFNP1%2BK4afk1FkPYtrFBHe52Fn%2F6n3rMGN5k%3D&h=3f94318e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/news/%E8%8F%AF%E7%82%BA%E6%93%9A%E5%A0%B1%E6%93%AC%E6%8E%A8%E6%96%B0%E6%AC%BE%E9%AB%98%E7%AB%AF%E6%89%8B%E6%A9%9F%E6%88%96%E4%B8%8D%E8%83%BD%E8%A3%9D-android-002827694.html</a>"},{"pid":"dbe17fefaca863a0b364a9be8e2ab60df10056d3","tid":1516624,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:31:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/fac